{"type":"message","id":"bd02060e","parentId":"a453cf60","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:30:12.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a61whrv5vebh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Daily Memory - 2026-03-19\n\n## Session with Bobby (initial meet/intro)\n\n- **Name:** Bobby Galletta\n- **Pronouns:** he/him\n- **Timezone:** America/New_York (EDT)\n- **Email:** rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- **Chat:** Telegram (8212808444)\n\n## About Emmy\n- I'm Emmy — Bobby's email assistant, share workspace with Dean\n- Model: Bobby requested MiniMax-M2.7 for me\n\n## Email Setup (IMPORTANT)\n- **gog CLI** (Google CLI) — WORKING OAuth access to Gmail\n- **himalaya CLI** — BROKEN (app-specific password \"mvbezpiqfnzzgomc\" no longer valid)\n- Bobby mentioned OAuth should work, but himalaya wasn't built with oauth2 support\n\n## Email Labels (from email-processor skill)\nAvailable labels: AI Tools, Finance & Bills, Gaming, Home Services, Job Search, Music & Beats, Newsletters, Personal, Security, Shopping & Orders, Social Media, Subscriptions\n\n## Xfinity Emails Today\nTwo emails from Xfinity (xfinity@account.xfinity.com):\n1. **Order confirmation** (18:10) — Confirmed updated Residential internet plan: 500 Mbps down/35 Mbps up, $95/mo. Label: Home Services\n2. **Complete your recent request** (18:00) — Follow-up asking to click link to continue a request (expires 72hrs). Label: Personal\n\n## Cron Jobs (observed)\n- Hourly Email Check — checks unlabeled emails, labels them, sends Telegram summary\n- Morning Brief — runs 5:30 AM ET daily\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774276212550}}
