{"type":"message","id":"b7c5ba27","parentId":"8bad581a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:30:15.018Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vn4gt0uib2qk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - Long-term Memory for Bobby's Assistant\n\nThis file stores important information about Bobby that should persist between sessions.\n\n---\n\n## About Bobby\n\n- **Name:** Bobby\n- **Husband:** Logan\n- **Location:** Knoxville, TN (37919)\n- **Setup:** MacBook Air\n\n---\n\n## Bobby's Preferences\n\n### Morning Brief\n- Weather: Knoxville (37919)\n- Bible verse with personal motivation\n- X/Twitter: Politics, OpenClaw tips, Making Money tips\n- Calendar: Family Calendar (iCloud)\n- Reminders: Default list\n\n### Email\n- Gmail: rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- Uses app password / OAuth\n\n### Apple Music\n- Default playlist: \"MY PLAYLIST\"\n\n---\n\n## Key Projects & Context\n\n- OpenClaw setup\n- Building morning brief skill\n- Camera stream (\"Dean's Eye\")\n- Research agent \"Richie\"\n\n---\n\n## Things Bobby Likes\n\n- Political content on X/Twitter\n- OpenClaw tips\n- Making money with AI/agents\n\n---\n\n## Important Notes\n\n- Bobby wants proactive assistance\n- Morning brief at 5:30 AM\n- Prefers Safari for browser automation (more reliable)\n\n---\n\n*Last updated: 2026-03-10*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774276215016}}
{"type":"message","id":"675ee78b","parentId":"b7c5ba27","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:30:30.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No specific TikTok context found. This is a fresh conversation starter. The cron job fired and I need to continue the conversation about AI-generated TikTok personas for making money.\n\nI should message Bobby on Telegram (8212808444) to start/continue this discussion. The cron reminder was about discussing:\n- Niche selection\n- Persona creation system\n- Tools\n- Content production workflow\n\nLet me craft a message that kicks off this conversation.","thinkingSignature":"93879bbfa6a69fec8539daec4dcc861785dd26bca5d20dde76ab73051ea6ecf7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nvjqyruopi1h_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"8212808444","message":"Hey Bobby! 👋 TikTok persona discussion time — you wanted to talk about building AI-generated TikTok personas for making money.\n\nHere's a quick framework to get us started:\n\n**🎯 Niche Selection**\nWhat niches are you targeting? Popular money-making TikTok niches:\n- Finance/money tips (high CPM)\n- AI tools & productivity\n- Relationship advice\n- Fitness/health\n- Tech reviews\n\n**🧑‍💻 Persona Creation System**\nKey elements:\n- Character archetype (teacher, gossip, mentor, entertainer)\n- Voice & speaking style\n- Visual identity (colors, overlays, on-screen elements)\n- Content pillars (3-5 recurring themes)\n\n**🛠️ Tools for AI-Generated Content**\n- **HeyGen** — AI avatars & voice sync\n- **InVideo** — AI video editing\n- **Opus Clip** — Long→Shorts repurposing\n- **11 ElevenLabs** — Voice cloning\n- **CapCut** — Auto-editing templates\n\n**📺 Content Production Workflow**\n1. Pick niche → Define persona\n2. Script batch (AI generate 10-20 at once)\n3. Generate avatar/lip-sync videos\n4. Auto-edit with CapCut templates\n5. Schedule & publish\n\nWhat direction are you thinking? Which niche interests you most?"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1548,"output":419,"cacheRead":18498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20465,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774276215019}}
